data.description: WELCOME TO THIS IMMACULATE 3 BEDROOM 2 BATHROOM HOME IN DESIRABLE LOCKMAR ESTATES! This stunning home features an open floor plan with a NEW ROOF and new plumbing! Privacy awaits you as you do not have neighbors behind you plus an oversized lot! Fruit trees too! Vaulted cathedral ceilings enhance the light, bright and airy feel to this home as well as a split floor plan! There is plenty of room for the whole family here too! Relax and enjoy the Florida lifestyle on your screened-in lanai! Additional features of this home are an updated chefs dream kitchen with ample storage and cabinets, updated bathrooms, new exterior/interior paint and much more! A wood burning fireplace adds to the ambiance and appeal of this masterpiece home! COME SEE THIS HOME TODAY!
